b'[<p><i><b>UFC on Fox: Diaz vs. Miller</b></i> (also known as <i><b>UFC on Fox 3</b></i>) was a mixed martial arts event held by the <a href="/wiki/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship" title="Ultimate Fighting Championship">Ultimate Fighting Championship</a> on May 5, 2012 at the <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/IZOD_Center" title="IZOD Center">IZOD Center</a> in <a href="/wiki/East_Rutherford,_New_Jersey" title="East Rutherford, New Jersey">East Rutherford</a>, <a href="/wiki/New_Jersey" title="New Jersey">New Jersey</a>.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-UFCFox3_2-0"><a href="#cite_note-UFCFox3-2">[2]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p><a href="/wiki/Dennis_Hallman" title="Dennis Hallman">Dennis Hallman</a> was expected to face <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/Tony_Ferguson_(fighter)" title="Tony Ferguson (fighter)">Tony Ferguson</a> at the event, but Hallman was forced out of the bout with an injury and replaced by <a href="/wiki/Thiago_Tavares" title="Thiago Tavares">Thiago Tavares</a>.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-HallmanOut/TavaresIn_3-0"><a href="#cite_note-HallmanOut/TavaresIn-3">[3]</a></sup> Tavares himself was also forced from the bout with an injury and replaced by <a href="/wiki/Michael_Johnson_(fighter)" title="Michael Johnson (fighter)">Michael Johnson</a>.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-TavaresOut/JohnsonIn_4-0"><a href="#cite_note-TavaresOut/JohnsonIn-4">[4]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p><a href="/wiki/Darren_Uyenoyama" title="Darren Uyenoyama">Darren Uyenoyama</a> was expected to face <a href="/wiki/John_Dodson_(fighter)" title="John Dodson (fighter)">John Dodson</a> at the event, but Uyenoyama was forced out of the bout and was replaced by promotional newcomer <a href="/wiki/Tim_Elliott" title="Tim Elliott">Tim Elliott</a>.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-5"><a href="#cite_note-5">[5]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p><a href="/wiki/Johnny_Bedford" title="Johnny Bedford">Johnny Bedford</a> was expected to face <a href="/wiki/Nick_Denis" title="Nick Denis">Nick Denis</a> at the event, but Bedford was forced out of the bout with an injury and replaced by <a href="/wiki/Roland_Delorme" title="Roland Delorme">Roland Delorme</a>.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-BedfordOut/DelormeIn_6-0"><a href="#cite_note-BedfordOut/DelormeIn-6">[6]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p>During the official weigh ins, <a href="/wiki/John_Lineker" title="John Lineker">John Lineker</a> failed to make the flyweight limit, coming in one pound over.  Lineker was fined and his bout with <a href="/wiki/Louis_Gaudinot" title="Louis Gaudinot">Louis Gaudinot</a> was contested at a catchweight of 127 pounds.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-7"><a href="#cite_note-7">[7]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p>Fighters were awarded $65,000 bonuses.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-8"><a href="#cite_note-8">[8]</a></sup>\n</p>]'